						<summary>

						<p>Hero-stone set up near the Kalmaṭha outside the village.</p>						

						<p>15th century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This damaged and wornout inscription seems to record the death of the son (name lost) of Kallaya-sāhaṇi. Mentions <hi rend="italic">Mahāpradhāna</hi> Sōva[rasa]. In characters of about 15th century A.D.</p>						

						</summary>
